<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>كِتَابُ الطَّهَارَةِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> المِيَاهُ ثَلَاثَةٌ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">الأَوَّلُ:</span> طَهُورٌ، وَهُوَ البَاقِي عَلَى خِلْقَتِهِ،<span class="c5"> وَمِنْهُ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> مَكْرُوهٌ؛ كَمُتَغَيِّرٍ بِغَيْرِ مُمَازِجٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَمُحَرَّمٌ، لَا يَرْفَعُ الحَدَثَ وَيُزِيلُ الخَبَثَ،<span class="c5"> وَهُوَ:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- المَغْصُوبُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَغَيْرُ بِئْرِ النَّاقَةِ مِنْ آبارِ <span class="c2">(١)</span> ثَمُودَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">الثَّانِي:</span> طَاهِرٌ، لَا يَرْفَعُ الحَدَثَ وَلَا يُزِيلُ الخَبَثَ،<span class="c5"> وَهُوَ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- المُتَغَيِّرُ بِمُمَازِجٍ طَاهِرٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَمِنْهُ:</span> يَسِيرٌ مُسْتَعْمَلٌ فِي رَفْعِ حَدَثٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">الثَّالِثُ:</span> نَجِسٌ، يَحْرُمُ اسْتِعْمَالُهُ مُطْلَقاً إِلَّا لِضَرُورَةٍ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>،<span class="c5"> وَهُوَ:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- مَا تَغَيَّرَ بِنَجَاسَةٍ فِي غَيْرِ مَحَلِّ تَطْهِيرٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- أَوْ لَاقَاهَا فِي غَيْرِهِ وَهُوَ يَسِيرٌ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) سقطت من (ب) و (ج) و (د).<br>(٢) قوله: (إلا لضرورة) سقطت من (أ) و (ب) و (ج).</p> </div>